---
import LocationServicePage from '~/components/pages/LocationServicePage.astro';
---

<LocationServicePage city="Ada" slug="electrician-ada-mi" county="Kent County, MI">
  <section class="container section-pad">
    <h2>About Electrical Service in Ada, MI</h2>
    <p>
      Ada has a strong custom-home and equestrian presence, which means electrical scope often goes beyond the standard
      residential package — 400A services, decorative lighting, barn power, and outbuilding feeders are routine here.
      New construction coordination with framing, finish, and mechanical trades is part of the job.
    </p>
    <p>
      Custom homes in Ada tend to need carefully designed electrical packages: layout-driven lighting, dedicated
      circuits for high-end appliances and AV, generator integration, and EV charging — sometimes for two vehicles.
      Horse barns and outbuildings add their own requirements: damp-rated fixtures, properly placed receptacles, and
      switching that makes daily use easy.
    </p>

    <h3>Common Ada Projects</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>400A residential service for custom homes with EV, generator, and electric heat</li>
      <li>Decorative lighting and dimming for finished spaces</li>
      <li>Horse barn electrical: stall lighting, dedicated circuits, exterior fixtures</li>
      <li>Outbuilding feeders and subpanels</li>
      <li>EV charger installation, sometimes dual-charger setups</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Ada-Specific Service Pages</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/panel-upgrades-ada-mi">Electrical panel upgrades in Ada, MI</a></li>
      <li><a href="/ev-chargers-ada-mi">EV charger installation in Ada, MI</a></li>
      <li><a href="/electrical-repairs-ada-mi">Electrical repairs in Ada, MI</a></li>
      <li><a href="/lighting-ada-mi">Lighting installation in Ada, MI</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Recent Work in Ada</h2>
      <article class="service-card" style="display: block;">
        <img
          src="/images/gallery/Light%20Fixture.webp"
          alt="Custom home decorative lighting installation in Ada, MI"
          width="800"
          height="600"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          style="border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 100%; height: auto;"
        />
        <h3>
          <a href="/projects/ada-mi-custom-home-and-horse-barn"> Custom Home and Horse Barn — 400A Service </a>
        </h3>
        <p>
          Custom home and matching custom horse barn on a single 400A service. Decorative lighting in the home,
          code-compliant stall lighting and barn power, and a clean finish across both buildings.
        </p>
        <p><a href="/projects/ada-mi-custom-home-and-horse-barn">View project →</a></p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</LocationServicePage>
